searchData={"items":[{"type":"module","title":"Raggio.Schema","doc":"Composable schema definition and validation library.\n\nRaggio.Schema provides a function-based API for defining data schemas and validating data.\nType constructors accept keyword options for constraints:\n\n    Schema.string(min: 3, max: 20)\n    Schema.integer(min: 0, max: 100)\n    Schema.list(Schema.string(), min: 1, unique: true)\n\n    Schema.struct([\n      {:name, Schema.string(min: 1)},\n      {:age, Schema.integer(min: 0)},\n      {:email, Schema.optional(Schema.string(pattern: Schema.email()))}\n    ])\n\nCore Constraints: min, max, pattern, unique\nField Descriptors: optional/1, nullable/1, default: keyword option","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.t/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#t:t/0"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.validation_error/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#t:validation_error/0"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.validation_result/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#t:validation_result/0"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.annotate/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#annotate/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.atom/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#atom/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.boolean/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#boolean/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.date/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#date/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.datetime/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#datetime/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.decimal/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#decimal/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.email/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#email/0"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.float/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#float/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.integer/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#integer/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.list/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#list/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.literal/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#literal/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.literal/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#literal/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.literal/3","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#literal/3"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.literal/4","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#literal/4"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.literal/5","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#literal/5"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.nullable/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#nullable/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.optional/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#optional/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.record/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#record/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.string/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#string/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.struct/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#struct/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.tuple/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#tuple/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.union/1","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#union/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.url/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#url/0"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.uuid/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#uuid/0"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.validate/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#validate/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.validate/3","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#validate/3"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.validate!/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.html#validate!/2"},{"type":"module","title":"Raggio.Schema.Adapters.BigQuery","doc":"BigQuery DDL exporter for Raggio.Schema.\n\nConverts Raggio.Schema definitions to BigQuery standard SQL DDL.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Adapters.BigQuery.html"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Adapters.BigQuery.to_ddl/3","doc":"Converts a Raggio.Schema to BigQuery DDL.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Adapters.BigQuery.html#to_ddl/3"},{"type":"function","title":"Examples - Raggio.Schema.Adapters.BigQuery.to_ddl/3","doc":"schema = Raggio.Schema.struct([\n      {:id, Raggio.Schema.integer()},\n      {:email, Raggio.Schema.string()}\n    ])\n    \n    BigQuery.to_ddl(schema, \"users\")\n    # => \"CREATE TABLE `users` (\\n  id INT64,\\n  email STRING\\n)\"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Adapters.BigQuery.html#to_ddl/3-examples"},{"type":"module","title":"Raggio.Schema.Filter","doc":"Represents a single validation constraint.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Filter.html"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.Filter.t/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Filter.html#t:t/0"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Filter.new/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Filter.html#new/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Filter.validate/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Filter.html#validate/2"},{"type":"module","title":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema","doc":"SheetSchema spreadsheet importer for Raggio.Schema.\n\nImports schema definitions from CSV/TSV format with columns:\n- field_name (required): Field identifier\n- type (required): Type expression (string, integer, list(string), etc.)\n- required (optional): Boolean (true/false/yes/no/1/0)\n- constraints (optional): Pipe-separated constraint functions\n- description (optional): Human-readable documentation\n- example (optional): Example value\n- default (optional): Default value\n- parent_path (optional): Dot-notation nesting path","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.html"},{"type":"module","title":"Example - Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema","doc":"{:ok, code} = SheetSchema.from_csv(\"schema.csv\")\n    IO.puts(code)","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.html#module-example"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.import_option/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.html#t:import_option/0"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.validation_error/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.html#t:validation_error/0"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.from_csv/1","doc":"Import schema from CSV file.\n\nReturns generated Elixir code as string.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.html#from_csv/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.from_csv/2","doc":"Import schema from CSV file with options.\n\nOptions:\n- `format: boolean()` - Format generated code (default: true)\n- `module_name: string()` - Wrap in module definition","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.html#from_csv/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.validate/1","doc":"Validate SheetSchema format without generating code.\n\nReturns `:ok` or list of validation errors with row numbers.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Importer.SheetSchema.html#validate/1"},{"type":"module","title":"Raggio.Schema.Validator","doc":"Core validation logic for Raggio.Schema.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Validator.html"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Validator.validate/2","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Validator.html#validate/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.Validator.validate/3","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.Validator.html#validate/3"},{"type":"exception","title":"Raggio.Schema.CompositionError","doc":"Error raised when composing incompatible schemas.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.CompositionError.html"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.CompositionError.t/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.CompositionError.html#t:t/0"},{"type":"exception","title":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError","doc":"Error raised when validation fails.","ref":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError.html"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError.error_detail/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError.html#t:error_detail/0"},{"type":"type","title":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError.t/0","doc":"","ref":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError.html#t:t/0"},{"type":"function","title":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError.message/1","doc":"Callback implementation for  Exception.message/1 .","ref":"Raggio.Schema.ValidationError.html#message/1"},{"type":"extras","title":"Raggio.Schema","doc":"# Raggio.Schema\n\nComposable schema definition and validation library for Elixir.","ref":"readme.html"},{"type":"extras","title":"Purpose - Raggio.Schema","doc":"Raggio.Schema provides a composable, function-based API for defining data schemas and validating data without complex macro syntax. Build type-safe schemas using the pipe operator and pure functions.","ref":"readme.html#purpose"},{"type":"extras","title":"Installation - Raggio.Schema","doc":"Add `raggio_schema` to your list of dependencies in `mix.exs`:\n\n```elixir\ndef deps do\n  [\n    {:raggio_schema, \"~> 0.1.0\"}\n  ]\nend\n```","ref":"readme.html#installation"},{"type":"extras","title":"Quick Example - Raggio.Schema","doc":"```elixir\n# Define schema\nuser_schema = Raggio.Schema.struct([\n  {:name, Raggio.Schema.string()},\n  {:age, Raggio.Schema.integer() |> Raggio.Schema.positive()}\n])\n\n# Validate data\ncase Raggio.Schema.validate(user_schema, %{name: \"Alice\", age: 30}) do\n  {:ok, data} -> {:ok, data}\n  {:error, errors} -> {:error, errors}\nend\n```","ref":"readme.html#quick-example"},{"type":"extras","title":"More Examples - Raggio.Schema","doc":"See the `examples/raggio_schema/` directory for working, compilable examples demonstrating various patterns and use cases.","ref":"readme.html#more-examples"},{"type":"extras","title":"Changelog","doc":"# Changelog\n\nAll notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.\n\nThe format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),\nand this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).\n\n## [0.1.0] - 2026-01-13","ref":"changelog.html"},{"type":"extras","title":"Added - Changelog","doc":"- Initial release\n- Composable schema definition API with `struct/1`, `string/0`, `integer/0`, `float/0`, `boolean/0`\n- Type validation with `positive/0`, `negative/0`, `min/1`, `max/1`, `range/2`\n- Collection types with `array/1`, `map/2`\n- Union types with `union/1` and enum validation with `enum/1`\n- Optional fields with `optional/1` and default values with `default/2`\n- Nested schema support\n- Custom validator composition with `custom/1`\n- BigQuery schema export adapter\n- Sheet schema import adapter\n- Comprehensive validation error reporting","ref":"changelog.html#added"}],"proglang":"elixir","content_type":"text/markdown","producer":{"name":"ex_doc","version":"0.39.3"}}